Package CssHandlers

package CssHandlers
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CssAddEditForm
    CssAddEditForm is an HTTP handler for serving CSS styles for the add and edit forms.
    CssLoginRegistrationForm
    CssLoginRegistrationForm is an HTTP handler for serving CSS styles for the login and the registration forms.
    CssResultPage
    CssResultPage is an HTTP handler for serving CSS styles for result pages (example:after adding or deleting a food product, after creating an account etc.).
    CssTable
    CssTable is an HTTP handler for serving CSS styles for pages that contains a table.
